Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Minimun time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimun resolution time of cases after 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' for cases that are resubmitted and approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to the next 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' until the case is closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimun time until a case is resubmitted after 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases that are resubmitted and change the approval path
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
